# Sūra XXXVII.: Ṣāffāt, or Those Ranged in Ranks.

### Section 5

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_139.gif)

139. Wa-inna yoonusa lamina almursaleen**a**

139\. So also was Jonah  
Among those sent (by Us).

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_140.gif)

140. I<u>th</u> abaqa il<u>a</u> alfulki almash<u>h</u>oon**i**

140\. When he ran away  
(Like a slave from captivity)  
To the ship (fully) laden,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_141.gif)

141. Fas<u>a</u>hama fak<u>a</u>na mina almud<u>h</u>a<u>d</u>een**a**

141\. He (agreed to) cast lots,  
And he was condemned:

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_142.gif)

142. Fa**i**ltaqamahu al<u>h</u>ootu wahuwa muleem**un**

142\. Then the big Fish  
Did swallow him,  
And he had done  
Acts worthy of blame.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_143.gif)

143. Falawl<u>a</u> annahu k<u>a</u>na mina almusabbi<u>h</u>een**a**

143\. Had it not been  
That he (repented and)  
Glorified God,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_144.gif)

144. Lalabitha fee ba<u>t</u>nihi il<u>a</u> yawmi yubAAathoon**a**

144\. He would certainly have  
Remained inside the Fish  
Till the Day of Resurrection.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_145.gif)

145. Fanaba<u>th</u>n<u>a</u>hu bi**a**lAAar<u>a</u>-i wahuwa
saqeem**un**

145\. But We cast him forth  
On the naked shore  
In a state of sickness,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_146.gif)

146. Waanbatn<u>a</u> AAalayhi shajaratan min yaq<u>t</u>een**in**

146\. And We caused to grow,  
Over him, a spreading plant  
Of the Gourd kind.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_147.gif)

147. Waarsaln<u>a</u>hu il<u>a</u> mi-ati alfin aw yazeedoon**a**

147\. And We sent him  
(On a mission)  
To a hundred thousand  
(Men) or more.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_148.gif)

148. Fa<u>a</u>manoo famattaAAn<u>a</u>hum il<u>a</u> <u>h</u>een**in**

148\. And they believed;  
So We permitted them  
To enjoy (their life)  
For a while.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_149.gif)

149. Fa**i**staftihim alirabbika alban<u>a</u>tu walahumu albanoon**a**

149\. Now ask them their opinion:  
Is it that thy Lord  
Has (only) daughters, and they  
Have sons?—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_150.gif)

150. Am khalaqn<u>a</u> almal<u>a</u>-ikata in<u>a</u>than wahum
sh<u>a</u>hidoon**a**

150\. Or that We created  
The angels female, and they  
Are witnesses (thereto)?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_151.gif)

151. Al<u>a</u> innahum min ifkihim layaqooloon**a**

151\. Is it not that they  
Say, from their own invention,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_152.gif)

152. Walada All<u>a</u>hu wa-innahum lak<u>ath</u>iboon**a**

152\. "God has begotten children"?  
But they are liars!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_153.gif)

153. A<u>st</u>af<u>a</u> alban<u>a</u>ti AAal<u>a</u> albaneen**a**

153\. Did He (then) choose  
Daughters rather than sons?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_154.gif)

154. M<u>a</u> lakum kayfa ta<u>h</u>kumoon**a**

154\. What is the matter  
With you? How judge ye?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_155.gif)

155. Afal<u>a</u> ta<u>th</u>akkaroon**a**

155\. Will ye not then  
Receive admonition?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_156.gif)

156. Am lakum sul<u>ta</u>nun mubeen**un**

156\. Or have ye  
An authority manifest?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_157.gif)

157. Fa/too bikit<u>a</u>bikum in kuntum <u>sa</u>diqeen**a**

157\. Then bring ye your Book  
(Of authority) if ye be  
Truthful!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_158.gif)

158. WajaAAaloo baynahu wabayna aljinnati nasaban walaqad AAalimati
aljinnatu innahum lamu<u>hd</u>aroon**a**

158\. And they have invented  
A blood-relationship  
Between Him and the Jinns:  
But the Jinns know  
(Quite well) that they  
Have indeed to appear  
(Before His Judgment-seat)!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_159.gif)

159. Sub<u>ha</u>na All<u>a</u>hi AAamm<u>a</u> ya<u>s</u>ifoon**a**

159\. Glory to God! (He is free)  
From the things they ascribe  
(To Him)!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_160.gif)

160. Ill<u>a</u> AAib<u>a</u>da All<u>a</u>hi almukhla<u>s</u>een**a**

160\. Not (so do) the Servants  
Of God, sincere and devoted.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_161.gif)

161. Fa-innakum wam<u>a</u> taAAbudoon**a**

161\. For, verily, neither ye  
Nor those ye worship—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_162.gif)

162. M<u>a</u> antum AAalayhi bif<u>a</u>tineen**a**

162\. Can lead (any)  
Into temptation  
Concerning God,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_163.gif)

163. Ill<u>a</u> man huwa <u>sa</u>li alja<u>h</u>eem**i**

163\. Except such as are  
(Themselves) going to  
The blazing Fire!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_164.gif)

164. Wam<u>a</u> minn<u>a</u> ill<u>a</u> lahu maq<u>a</u>mun
maAAloom**un**

164\. (Those ranged in ranks say):  
"Not one of us but has  
A place appointed;

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_165.gif)

165. Wa-inn<u>a</u> lana<u>h</u>nu a**l**<u>ssa</u>ffoon**a**

165\. "And we are verily  
Ranged in ranks (for service);

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_166.gif)

166. Wa-inn<u>a</u> lana<u>h</u>nu almusabbi<u>h</u>oon**a**

166\. "And we are verily those  
Who declare (God's) glory!"

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_167.gif)

167. Wa-in k<u>a</u>noo layaqooloon**a**

167\. And there were those  
Who said,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_168.gif)

168. Law anna AAindan<u>a</u> <u>th</u>ikran mina al-awwaleen**a**

168\. "If only we had had  
Before us a Message  
From those of old,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_169.gif)

169. Lakunn<u>a</u> AAib<u>a</u>da All<u>a</u>hi
almukhla<u>s</u>een**a**

169\. "We should certainly have  
Been Servants of God,  
Sincere (and devoted)!"

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_170.gif)

170. Fakafaroo bihi fasawfa yaAAlamoon**a**

170\. But (now that the Qur-ān  
Has come), they reject it:  
But soon will they know!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_171.gif)

171. Walaqad sabaqat kalimatun<u>a</u> liAAib<u>a</u>din<u>a</u>
almursaleen**a**

171\. Already has Our Word  
Been passed before (this)  
To Our Servants sent (by Us),

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_172.gif)

172. Innahum lahumu alman<u>s</u>ooroon**a**

172\. That they would certainly  
Be assisted,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_173.gif)

173. Wa-inna jundan<u>a</u> lahumu algh<u>a</u>liboon**a**

173\. And that Our forces,—  
They surely must conquer.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_174.gif)

174. Fatawalla AAanhum <u>h</u>att<u>a</u> <u>h</u>een**in**

174\. So turn thou away  
From them for a little while,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_175.gif)

175. Waab<u>s</u>irhum fasawfa yub<u>s</u>iroon**a**

175\. And watch them (how  
They fare), and they soon  
Shall see (how thou farest)!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_176.gif)

176. AfabiAAa<u>tha</u>bin<u>a</u> yastaAAjiloon**a**

176\. Do they wish (indeed)  
To hurry on our Punishment?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_177.gif)

177. Fa-i<u>tha</u> nazala bis<u>ah</u>atihim fas<u>a</u>a
<u>s</u>ab<u>ah</u>u almun<u>th</u>areen**a**

177\. But when it descends  
Into the open space  
Before them, evil will be  
The morning for those who  
Were warned (and heeded not)!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_178.gif)

178. Watawalla AAanhum <u>h</u>att<u>a</u> <u>h</u>een**in**

178\. So turn thou away  
From them for a little while,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_179.gif)

179. Waab<u>s</u>ir fasawfa yub<u>s</u>iroon**a**

179\. And watch (how they fare)  
And they soon shall see  
(How thou farest)!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_180.gif)

180. Sub<u>ha</u>na rabbika rabbi alAAizzati AAamm<u>a</u>
ya<u>s</u>ifoon**a**

180\. Glory to thy Lord,  
The Lord of Honour  
And Power! (He is free)  
From what they ascribe  
(To Him)!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_181.gif)

181. Wasal<u>a</u>mun AAal<u>a</u> almursaleen**a**

181\. And Peace on the apostles!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/037/037_182.gif)

182. Wa**a**l<u>h</u>amdu lill<u>a</u>hi rabbi alAA<u>a</u>lameen**a**

182\. And Praise to God,  
The Lord and Cherisher  
Of the Worlds.

